Name: Guide 82" Sofa
Description: The Guide 82-inch Sofa by Blu Dot is a sleek and modern centerpiece for your living space. With its minimalist design, plush cushions, and durable construction, it offers both style and comfort. The slim metal legs add a touch of elegance, making it a versatile addition to any home décor. Dimensions: 31” Height, 82” Length
Colors: Sanford Oatmeal, Coffee Velvet, Moss Velvet

Name: Windsor Cherry Grandfather Clock
Description: Elevate your home décor with the Andrako Clock II, boasting a Windsor Cherry finish and intricate design that adds sophistication to any space. Crafted with a sturdy wood frame and adjustable levelers, this American-made masterpiece stands at 88.5 inches tall, features high-precision chimes, and offers versatile volume control for an enchanting ambiance day and night. Experience the timeless elegance of Howard Miller's specialty furnishings, offering a range of exquisite pieces for your home, from curio cabinets to adjustable height desks. Dimensions: 31"W x 94.5"H

Name: 31.5" Lift Top Coffee Table with Storage
Description: Introducing our sleek Coffee Table with Storage: the perfect blend of style and functionality. Keep your living space tidy with hidden compartments while adding a modern touch to your décor.

Name: Ergonomic Wicker Papasan Chair
Description: Experience ultimate comfort and versatility with our ergonomic Papasan chair, featuring a sturdy metal frame and expertly woven resin wicker for durability. Enjoy heavenly relaxation with the plush 6 3/4-inch thick cushion, complete with 360-degree swivel capability and easy assembly for a seamless addition to any room.

Name: Arched Full Length Mirror
Description: Enhance your space with our Aluminum Alloy Frame Full Length Mirror, featuring newly upgraded Nano Glass for superior clarity and durability. With a sleek 0.23" wide frame and a generous size of 64" x 21", this versatile mirror doubles as both a functional piece and an elegant addition to any room.
